===Pronunciation=== 
* {{IPA|/əˈkɪliːz/|lang=en}} 

===Proper noun===
{{en-proper noun}}

# {{context|Greek mythology}} semi-divine [[hero]], son of [[Peleus]] and the nymph [[Thetis]], prince and leader of the Myrmidons; great warrior of the Achaean (Greek) camp, killed in the [[Trojan War]]; central character of the [[w:Iliad|Iliad]].

